07:05.758 --> 07:09.178
[grunting]

07:09.262 --> 07:12.306
Okay, that's one sock on.

07:13.015 --> 07:15.184
Now for the hard one.

07:15.268 --> 07:16.894
Ol' lefty.

07:16.978 --> 07:19.772
[grunting]

07:19.856 --> 07:22.900
