07:30.158 --> 07:31.659
That's okay, Frank.

07:31.742 --> 07:34.787
We all waited in silence
for you to arrive.

07:36.581 --> 07:38.749
I've called you all in to tell you that,

07:38.833 --> 07:43.045
unfortunately, our profits have gone down
since the merger.

07:43.129 --> 07:46.591
It turns out the ad campaign
announcing our new identity

07:46.674 --> 07:49.218
