08:45.274 --> 08:46.526
[caws]

08:46.609 --> 08:49.070
Cool. Baby Jesus is feeding the hungry.

08:49.153 --> 08:53.407
Uh, yeah... Why don't you go in here
and get something for your father, hmm?

08:53.533 --> 08:56.077
Um, at the adult diaper store?

08:56.577 --> 08:59.288
